-- 01_customer_latest_channel.sql
```sql
WITH customer_latest_channel AS (
  SELECT 
    customer_id,
    channel,
    ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY customer_id ORDER BY attributed_at DESC) AS rn
  FROM customer_channels
)
SELECT 
  customer_id,
  channel
FROM customer_latest_channel
WHERE rn = 1

-- 02_revenue_by_attribution_channel.sql
```sql
SELECT 
  COALESCE(clc.channel, 'Unattributed') AS channel,
  COALESCE(s.city, 'Unknown') AS city,
  SUM(t.amount) AS total_revenue,
  COUNT(t.transaction_id) AS transaction_count,
  COUNT(DISTINCT t.customer_id) AS unique_customers
FROM transactions t
LEFT JOIN (
  WITH customer_latest_channel AS (
    SELECT 
      customer_id,
      channel,
      ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY customer_id ORDER BY attributed_at DESC) AS rn
    FROM customer_channels
  )
  SELECT customer_id, channel
  FROM customer_latest_channel
  WHERE rn = 1
) clc ON t.customer_id = clc.customer_id
LEFT JOIN stores s ON t.store_id = s.store_id
GROUP BY 
  COALESCE(clc.channel, 'Unattributed'),
  COALESCE(s.city, 'Unknown')
ORDER BY total_revenue DESC
